    "title": "Styling the Apple Pay Button Using CSS"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can experiment with styling and display of an Apple Pay button using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "link-3596712",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". To support devices running iOS 10 and macOS 10.12, use the CSS template sample code in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/displaying_apple_pay_buttons_using_css",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to draw the appropriate button.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To display an Apple Pay button set the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-webkit-appearance",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " CSS property of the element to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-apple-pay-button",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "See the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "link-3172425",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for more information.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "3596685",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Set the Button Size",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can resize the Apple Pay button to fit your website. The minimum displayed width and height for Apple Pay buttons are:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "For plain Apple Pay buttons the minimum displayed width is 100 points with a minimum displayed height of 30 points.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "For Apple Pay buttons that include a directive, such as “Buy with Apple Pay” or “Donate with Apple Pay,” the minimum displayed width is 140 points with a minimum displayed height of 30 points.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "3596686",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Set the Button Style",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can choose from several style options for the Apple Pay button to match your web site. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "link-3597397",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for guidance on which style to choose.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To display the black Apple Pay button, set the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-apple-pay-button-style",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " CSS property to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "black",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For example, the following example produces a black Apple Pay button:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<div style=\"display: inline-block;",
            "-webkit-appearance: -apple-pay-button;",
            "-apple-pay-button-type: plain;",
            "-apple-pay-button-style: black;\"",
            "lang=en></div>"
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3596711",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          },
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The color options for the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-apple-pay-button-style",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " CSS property are ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "white",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "white-outline",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "black",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "3596687",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Set the Button's Corner Radius",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You may configure the border radius of your Apple Pay button using the css ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "border-radius",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " property. The Apple Pay button supports a single ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "border-radius",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " value. If you set multiple ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "border-radius",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " properties, the largest value applies to all corners.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use border radius to match the styles of other buttons on your website. The default border radius is 4 points",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": ".",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In the following example, setting border radius to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0pt",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " displays a squared off button:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<div style=\"display: inline-block;",
            "border-radius: 0pt;",
            "-webkit-appearance: -apple-pay-button;",
            "-apple-pay-button-type: plain;",
            "-apple-pay-button-style: white-outline;\"",
            "lang=en></div>"
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3596709",
            "title": "Listing 2"
          },
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
